      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is a commercially maintained solver with formal SQA processes including automated regression testing, version-controlled source, and published release validation reports. All simulation input decks are stored under Git version control with commit hashes recorded in the simulation log. Gradation 2 requirements are fully satisfied."
