      },
      "rationale": "Numerical code verification is evidenced by ANSYS published benchmark suite results and an internal method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) study on laminar pipe flow confirming second-order spatial accuracy. Achieved level exceeds the MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/morrison-cou1-de-03",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
