      "factorStatus": "not-applicable",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters is not applicable because the CFD model and the validation experiment use identical input parameter sets (same geometry, same fluid properties, same boundary conditions). There is no translation or scaling between experimental and simulation inputs that would require equivalency justification."
